{"type": "article", "id": 12855, "title": "Bath °C 温度地图", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-31T07:34:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000211ErX4Vd7KcMHGzuva.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tBath °C是一个地图，名字来源是设计师的家乡英格兰的巴斯城。这个地图的不同之处在于它能够实时显示当地的温度状况。其工作原理是 TYVEK 织物是印刷了热变色油墨，油墨在不同温度下有不同的颜色。虽然现在电子地图和电子温度装备非常完善，但想想拿着一个这样的地图抛弃手机走在大街上，大概也蛮有趣的呢。这是<a href=\"http://camillahempleman.com/\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>，点击可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140534m50NguKpW6eTZQsv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140534DkWxP2QwcmbTS0EA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140535GsRSWQpKiDzI8jmh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1809291\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140536q7KXwxFOsVWDM8dH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.36674817\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140536GYOKiJVzP4TqlBDN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65892421\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140537LocBN8UHIYCjXT4A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.37041565\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140537Hs6UoWByPvZOrYkT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140538z6q49FkXupms31OK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140538w4bC1iKe7I8SRoPz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140539MLjTbUxJHlqKGZED.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79828851\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}